|-------|----------|-----|
| No security headers | High | Add `helmet()` |
| No input validation | High | Use `express-validator` |
| No rate limiting | Medium | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No error handling | High | Add try-catch & error middleware |
| Sensitive data exposure | Medium | Restrict email field |
| No request logging | Low | Add `morgan` |
| Missing env validation | Medium | Validate config on startup |

